  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Goal of this study is to test the hypothesis that repeated exposure to cycles of insufficient
      sleep increases susceptibility to a variety of disease states by progressively compromising
      the integrity of stress response systems.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
